text: Tobyl () is a city in the Kostanay Region of Kazakhstan. As of 2023, 28,453 people live in the city. This city is in the urban area of Kostanay. Tobyl was founded in 1863. At first it was named Zatobolsk (). It got city status in 2020. ==References== Category:1863 establishments Category:1860s establishments in Asia Category:Establishments in Kazakhstan Category:Cities and towns in Kazakhstan Category:Kostanay Region
